<<< For Sampling - Part 1 , Text prompt only.  

Extend Video Text prompts , use "Travel Prompt for Extend Video"

Travel Prompt Should be based on Number Of Extend.

One row = One Prompt

Press Enter to write another line = Text Prompt for another Video Extend.

E.g: 

726 Total Frames , FPS 25
= 29 Seconds video

If we use 121 frames for each sampling
= 6 video sampling times

No. 1 >>> Sampling - Part 1

No. 2-6 >>>> In Video Extend Loop

Framing & Lens: Tight medium close-up from chest upward, handheld dolly-in onto their embrace. Lighting: Metallic elevator walls scatter soft golden flares across her glittering red corset. Motion: The woman grabs the man’s face and crushes into a hard, urgent kiss, lips moving hungrily as her chest presses tight against his suit. Expression: The woman’s passion is raw, lips parted and demanding, eyes fluttering closed as she devours the moment. Aesthetic Control: Shallow depth with jittery handheld intimacy makes the kiss explosive.

Framing & Lens: Medium shot, angled from the side to show both figures full-body against mirrored panels. Lighting: Elevator lights shimmer against the crystals of her dress, each motion scattering sparks of red. Motion: The woman suddenly shoves the man against the opposite wall, her palm flattening on his chest as the elevator shakes slightly. Expression: The woman’s eyes blaze with fire, lips wet and parted, showing she is in full control. Aesthetic Control: Quick dolly-slide right intensifies the sudden power shift.
Framing & Lens: Wide shot from the corner, reflections multiplying their bodies across mirrored panels. Lighting: The glow turns moody, silver and amber tones highlighting every contour. Motion: The woman steps forward with slow, deliberate strides, hips swaying under the glittering corset, closing the gap between them. Expression: Her eyes never leave his — her look daring, lips curling slightly open with a heated breath as tension builds. Aesthetic Control: Slow dolly-in paired with a faint handheld sway mimics anticipation.
Framing & Lens: Medium close-up, slightly low angle as she leans into him again. Lighting: Golden reflections ripple across their locked bodies. Motion: The woman presses her hands firmly on his shoulders, sliding upward to grip his jaw as she crashes into another deep kiss, more controlled and powerful than before. Expression: Her intensity is unshakable — lips parted, eyes half-closed, consuming him and the frame at once. Aesthetic Control: Slow-motion overlay on the kiss impact makes it cinematic and trailer-like.
